snippet.title: WRC 10 FIA World Rally Championship - Launch Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
It’s time to be part of History and celebrate 50 years of WRC!

Relive the most iconic moments of the Championship through 19 historic events, drive through 6 legendary rallies included Acropolis Rally & Rallye Sanremo. The Career Mode has also been improved with a new livery editor and the chance to create your own team.

On PlayStation®5, feel the road on your DualSense™ controller with support for immersive haptic feedback and dynamic adaptive triggers!

#WRC10 is now available on PlayStation®5 and PlayStation®4.
